text: Marina's Destiny () is a 1953 Soviet drama movie directed by Isaak Shmaruk and Viktor Ivchenko."Судьба Марины"Судьба Марины (1953) It stars Yekaterina Litvinenko, Nikolai Gritsenko, and Tatyana Konyukhova. == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet movies Category:1953 movies Category:Soviet drama movies
